INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
=========================

polib download page: http://cheeseshop.python.org/pypi/polib/

Unix/BSD/Linux
--------------
If you have not done so yet, go to download page and download the source
distribution (polib-x-y-z.tar.gz).

$ tar xzfv polib-x.y.z.tar.gz
$ cd polib-x.y.z
$ python setup build
$ su - root
# python setup.py install

If your system support the rpm format you can alternatively download the
binary rpm (polib-x.y.z-k.rpm) and install it as usual.

Windows
-------
I recommend you download and install the binary package 
(polib-x.y.z.win32.exe).
